data.description: Gorgeous, move in ready, 3 bedroom 2 bath home, in the heart of Gretna. Many beautiful updates that include fresh paint, laminate flooring throughout, new carpet in 2 bedrooms, completely remodeled baths and upgraded lighting.  Spacious,  eat in kitchen, w/lots of cabinet and counter space, as well as walk in pantry!   Tastefully updated with white cabinets, brushed gold hardware and marble countertops. Built in desk area in breakfast nook! Large backyard great for entertaining! Flood policy $1967/YR. ***SELLERS ARE WILLING TO CONTRIBUTE TO A BUYERS RATE BUY DOWN W/ACCEPTABLE OFFER **THIS PROPERTY ALSO QUALIFIES FOR COMMUNITY LENDING 3% DOWN PAYMENT ASSISTANCE AND RATE REDUCTION.
